{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "李寻欢与铃铃来到郭嵩阳的尸体旁，李寻欢引导铃铃观察尸体上的二十六处剑伤，从中分析出荆无命剑法诡秘迅急、专走偏锋、自肋下反撩的特点。原来郭嵩阳是故意露出破绽让荆无命刺伤自己，只为让李寻欢看清对手的出手部位。铃铃深受感动，认识到世上确有轻生死、重义气的朋友。与此同时，上官金虹与荆无命也在分析郭嵩阳的意图，上官金虹指出荆无命已有情，这将削弱他的剑势。李寻欢将郭嵩阳安葬，铃铃主张将尸体挂回飞泉以继续迷惑对手，但李寻欢拒绝利用朋友的遗体。上官金虹判断李寻欢必在郭嵩阳处，但阻止荆无命回头，因为他看出荆无命已动情，不再是往日那个无情的杀手。本章以英雄与枭雄的对比收尾——英雄为义痴，枭雄为胜谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错，我毕竟还是来迟了一步。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他的人既然已死了，还能对你说话？……难道死人还能说话？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "有些话，用不着说出，我也可以听到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是……可是我怎么没有听见？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你也想知道他说了些什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "其实他也已将那些话告诉了你，只不过你没有注意去听而已，要知道死人告诉你的话，往往是最可贵的，因为这是他以自己生命换来的教训，你若能学会听死人说话，就可以多懂得许多事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是死人说的话我怎么能听得到呢？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "要学会听死人说的话，自然不是件容易事，但你若想多活几年，活得好些，就该法子学会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我……我不知道该怎么样学，你肯教我么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你再仔细听听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不但要用耳朵听，还要用眼睛听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你已听出了什么？看出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我……我看出他身上受了很多处伤，一共有十……十九处。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这些伤看来全都是剑伤，而且是被一柄很薄，很锐利的剑所伤。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "何以见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为他的伤口都很短，也不太深，显见只是一种兵刃的尖锋划破的。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "为什么一定是剑尖？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为刀尖枪尖都不可能有这么锐利。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "很好，你已学会很多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "由此可见，伤他的人一定是荆无命，因为上官金虾用的是龙凤环，不是剑。上官金虾也许并没有来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "也许他虽然来了，却没有出手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错，他的剑法不仅诡秘怪异，而且专走偏锋，每一剑出手的部位，都是对方绝不会想到的。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "由此可见荆无命出手的部位，必定在膝盖以下，用的就必定是腕力，我若只看到这伤口，也就想不到有人会在这种部位出手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不错，我若和人交手时，也不会将背对着人的。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "由此可见，他这些伤口一定是在两人身形交错时被荆无命所伤的，那么荆无命的剑只有从自己的肋下穿出，才能刺得到对方。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "自肋下出手本已不是常见的剑法，最怪的是，这每剑也是自下面反摩上来的，由此可见，荆无命必定已在两人身形交错时的那一瞬间，改变了握剑的姿势，可乘势将剑反刺而出，他变势与出手，显见只是一个动作，所以速度必定快得可怕！",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "原来他就是要告诉你这些话。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "若非如此，以他的武功，本不该受这么多处伤的。",
      "tone": "默然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "高手决斗，胜负往往只在一招之间，无论谁的剑法有了丝毫破隙，对方绝不会放过。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这我明白。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你想，嵩阳铁剑享誉武林二十年，单以剑法而论，已可算是当今天下数一数二的高手，又怎会在一场比斗中接连露出二十六处破缝，接连被对方刺伤了二十六处呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这……这倒的确有些奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "还有，荆无命的剑法既然那么毒辣，郭嵩阳这二十六处伤口都是轻伤，荆无命又怎会在他接连露出二十六次破缝后，还不能一剑刺死他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是呀……这是为什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "这只因郭嵩阳这二十六次破缝，都是故意露出的！",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "故意露出来的……他难道故意要荆无命刺伤他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错，就因为破缝是他故意露出来的，所以才每次都能及时闪避，所以他每次受的伤都不太重。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他这么做又是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "他这样做，只为了要将荆无命出手的部位告诉我！",
      "tone": "默然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "郭嵩阳的剑法如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "很好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "很好，在七大剑流掌门之上。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "但他与你交手时，露出的破缝却达二十六次之多。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "二十九次，有三次我未出手。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "不错，有三次你未出手，为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "因为那三次我若出手，便可要他的命！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你已看出他那些破缝是故意露出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "不错，所以我不愿他死得太快，我正好拿他来练剑！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你可知道他为何要故意露出那些破缝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "不知道，我没有去想。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他故意露出那些破缝，为的就是要你刺伤他。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他自知绝非我们敌手，所以才这么样做，好让李寻欢看了他身上的伤口，就可看出你出手的部位。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他自已知道李寻欢会跟着去的，你我现在若是回头，必定可以在那里找到他！",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你真的要将郭先生葬在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "一个人只要死得光荣，无论葬在哪里都是一样的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么你就不该将他葬在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不葬在这里，葬在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你应该将他再挂到那边的飞泉中。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "像上官金虾和荆无命这样的角色，迟早必定会看破郭先生的心意，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "荆无命自然不愿让你看破他剑法出手的部位，所以只要他们一想到这一点，就必定会立刻赶回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他们回来时，若是发现郭先生的尸体已不在原来的地方了，就必定会想到我们已来过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，等到他们和你交手时，就必定会将剑法改变了，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么郭先生的这一番心意岋非就白废了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你既是郭先生的好朋友，就应该让他死得有价值，所以你就不该将他埋葬在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你说的话，我也都想到过。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么你为何不将郭先生的尸身挂回原来的地方去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我不能这样做，他为我而死，我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就因他是为你而死的，所以你才一定要这样做，否则他岋非等于白死了么？他死得能瞪目么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我敢打赌，上官金虾和荆无命绝不会再回到这里来的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你要回去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我知道你久已想与小李飞刀决一死战，可是你现在绝不能去！",
      "tone": "压制",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你现在若是去了，必败无疑！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "你怎知我必败无疑？",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你已杀了郭嵩阳，杀气已减，李寻欢此刻却正是悲愤填膺，你若与他交手，在气势上你已输给他三分。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你已经一战，再加以长途跃涉，体力总难免更弱些，李寻欢在那里以逸待劳，又占了三分便宜。",
      "tone": "闪退",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你我若是联手，自然能致他死命，只不过……你怎知李寻欢是一个人去的？他若是和孙老儿在一起又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "凭他们两人，也未必能……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我早已告诉过你，我此次出江湗，只许胜，不许败，一定要有十二分的把握，才能出去！",
      "tone": "压制",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "何况，今日之你，已非昔日之你了！",
      "tone": "压制",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "我还是我！",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "但如今你有情。",
      "tone": "压制",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "有情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你能胜人，就因为你的无情，如今你既已有情，你的人与剑势都必要日渐软弱……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你从不动心，如今怎会有情，是谁打动了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "text": "没有人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_xia",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虾",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我也不想问你那人是谁，但你若想胜过别人，若想胜过李寻欢，就得恢复昔日的你，你若想恢复昔日的你，就得先杀了那令你动心的女人！",
      "tone": "压制",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 369
    }
